text
# Download Kioptrix Level 1 from vulnhub.com
# Boot VM → nmap -sV -sC 192.168.1.150
# Ports: 80(http), 139(netbios), 443(https), 1024(unfs)
2. OpenVAS Scan
text
# https://127.0.0.1:9392 → Scan 192.168.1.150
# Results: Drupal 7.31, Apache 1.3.20 flagged
3. Drupalgeddon2 Exploit (Above commands)
4. Post-Exploitation
text
